{NORTH thinks they should be in slam, and uses Stayman to check for a 4-4 Major fit.

When SOUTH announces four \Ss NORTH uses RKCB 4NT.

SOUTH's 5\S bid shows two Key Cards plus the \SQ.

This fills the holes in NORTH's hand nicely, so she bids 6\S.}

